high_descs: Turn left and walk forward, turning left again to face the white table
Pick up the furthest salt shaker from the white table
Turn left and walk a couple feet forward then turn left to face the counter
Open the top drawer and put the salt shaker in it
Walk up to the counter
Pick up the left most salt shaker from the counter
Turn around and step away from the counter then turn back around to face it
Open the top drawer and put the salt shaker in it
anns.task_desc: Put the salt shakers in the kitchen drawer

high_descs: Take a small step forward then turn left and walk to the wall then turn left.
Pick up the salt shaker that's furthest away from you.
Turn left and take a step forward then turn left and walk to the counter but leave enough room to pull open the drawer under the counter.
Open the drawer under the counter in front of you and put the salt shaker in the front right corner then close it.
Walk forward to the counter.
Grab the salt shaker that's near the left wall.
Back up a step so you can use the drawer under the counter.
Put this salt shaker in the drawer on the opposite side from the first salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the white table.
Pick up the white bottle next to the grey bowl.
Turn left and walk towards the white drawer
Place the bottle inside the drawer.
Close the white drawer.
Pick up the white bottle that is on top of the drawer cabinet.
Open the top drawer of the cabinet.
Place the bottle inside the drawer then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place the two bottles inside the top shelf of the white drawer.
